00:07:03.799 --> 00:07:09.880
for the submission. So we regard to the motivation why we need to

00:07:09.880 --> 00:07:14.200
use R or different R package for regulatory development, right. So

00:07:14.200 --> 00:07:19.239
for late stage, it's also have many of the space that have a

00:07:19.239 --> 00:07:23.760
lot of the nice package to be used for the clinical trial

00:07:23.760 --> 00:07:27.679
development. For example, R has been widely used for clinical

00:07:27.679 --> 00:07:30.160
