00:09:57.880 --> 00:10:02.520
member. So these are some motivations that drive us to

00:10:02.520 --> 00:10:07.440
explore more of a proper and compliant way of using R for

00:10:07.479 --> 00:10:12.960
regulatory submission. So for some background, the work here

00:10:12.960 --> 00:10:16.039
we're still trying to follow the ICH guidance, right? For the

