00:10:43.599 --> 00:10:47.559
discuss what's the concept for project management in clinical

00:10:47.559 --> 00:10:51.679
trial study space and provide some recommendations for that.

00:10:51.719 --> 00:10:54.880
And in the end, the most important part, once we complete

00:10:54.919 --> 00:10:59.000
analysis in R, we need to find a way to properly submit the

