00:24:48.560 --> 00:24:53.280
space, our version, our package version need to be managed. So

00:24:53.280 --> 00:24:57.680
ensure the reproducibility. And in addition, sometimes you may

00:24:57.680 --> 00:25:01.680
see some discrepancy for the results between operation

00:25:01.680 --> 00:25:06.359
system. This is also true for many other software, right. So

00:25:06.359 --> 00:25:11.520
the assumption is within an operation system, then we

00:25:11.599 --> 00:25:15.040
reproduce results. I think that's also the concept like

